description: AnrFunctionNR:  Table containing NR ANR function configuration parameters for different cells at specific timestamps.  Columns describe timestamp (dateTime), area (Area_Name), cell identifiers (CellId, Id2, Id3, Id4), data type and version (vsDataType, vsDataFormatVersion), and various ANR function configuration parameters (AnrFunctionNR.* and related columns like gNodebIdLength and anrStateNR).
